Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.47,0:00:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉莫洛克號 距Telemothy躍遷開始還有40秒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.34,0:00:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 不能就這樣把希迪亞斯也帶回去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.18,0:00:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.01,0:00:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你單獨回艦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.80,0:00:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來拖住那些傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.64,0:00:22.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庫蓋爾中校 這是違反軍令
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.84,0:00:24.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還年輕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.48,0:00:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會殺掉比我更多的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.76,0:00:28.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我作為軍人的判斷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.66,0:00:31.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願人類銀河同盟榮光長存
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.72,0:00:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保重了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.84,0:00:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中校！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.18,0:00:49.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.16,0:01:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警告
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.33,0:01:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本機已進入行星引力圈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.31,0:01:28.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.88,0:01:32.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即將接觸行星大氣層
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.26,0:01:36.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請選擇闖入或撤離
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.52,0:01:37.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然是行星
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.40,0:01:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對可觀測天體進行搜索比對
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.57,0:01:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.65,0:01:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,匹配記錄一條
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.44,0:01:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斷定為太陽系第三行星 地球
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.06,0:01:54.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然是…地球！
